title: Shock as Orbán allies buy Hungary’s most-read newspaper
summary: Blikk, a popular tabloid with approximately 3 million online monthly readers, has been acquired by the pro-Orbán media group Indamedia. This acquisition is part of Indamedia's strategy to strengthen its media presence. The move highlights the ongoing consolidation within Hungary's media landscape.
